Give the user the capability of setting text bounds to include or exclude areas. By default everything would be included.
For example
stripper.exclude( new Rectangle( 0,0, 999999, 100 ) );
would exclude the bottom 100 units(pixels)
stripper.include( new Rectangle( 0,0, 999999, 100 ) );
would only extract the bottom 100 units.
Maybe allow named regions for screen scraping capabilities. For example
stripper.addNamedRegion( "First Name", new Rectangle( 100,100,100,100 ) );
would keep track of all characters in the area and make then available to be retrieved after extraction.
String firstName = getNamedRegion( "First Name" );
It would clear the named region value by default for each page.

